data.description: 2 GARAGES, 3 LOTS, Bring your toys, no hoa! This  home with sparkling POOL is also on 3 WATERFRONT lots with NEW ROOF plus NEW AC! This magnificent 3/2.5/3 car garage estate offers an additional vacant lot and additional concrete stand alone 4 car garage with a 2 car garage bay door, luxurious living, unparalleled privacy, and breathtaking views that will leave you mesmerized.Hurry to see this exceptional waterfront property situated on three expansive lots WITH A DETACHED 4 CAR GARAGE!! A sparkling heated Pebble Tec pool with shallow sundeck feature, this home provides the ultimate haven for those who appreciate the finer things in life. Step inside and be captivated by the grandeur and elegance of this residence. The main living area features soaring ceilings, an abundance of natural light, and panoramic windows that showcase the serene waterfront vistas. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and gourmet kitchen, creating a perfect space for entertaining guests or enjoying quality time with loved ones.The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, wood cabinetry, and a breakfast bar with rich Granite countertop space. Whether you're creating culinary masterpieces or enjoying casual meals with family, this kitchen is sure to impress.The master suite is a private sanctuary, complete with a spacious bedroom, a luxurious ensuite bathroom with roman shower, dual sinks,seperate soaking tub and stunning views of the water. Additional well-appointed bedrooms provide comfort and privacy for family and guests. The separate 2.5 garage ( to left of home on lot 55) offers 9 ft door for a big boat, ample parking space for at least 5 cars between both attached 3 and detached 2.5. With so much extra room for storage, this property package is perfect for car enthusiasts or those with extra recreational vehicles or perhaps consider building an attached home, lots of possibilities . Step outside to the sprawling outdoor oasis, where you'll find a beautiful pool surrounded by lush landscaping, creating a resort-like atmosphere. Imagine relaxing by the poolside, soaking in the sun, and savoring the peaceful waterfront ambiance. New ac, well system, separate oversized shed with electric and rollup door plus an upcoming 44k roof with 35 year guarantee paid by seller prior to closing, you will enjoy peace of mind with this unique oasis! Located in a neighborhood of beautiful homes, this property offers a one of a kind opportunity to own an expansive estate, providing ultimate privacy while still being just a short distance from the city's amenities and attractions. Embrace the waterfront lifestyle with this exceptional property . Schedule a private tour and experience the luxury, privacy, and breathtaking views that this remarkable home has to offer.
